      "message": "Yeah I have the same concern but I think the possibility should be pretty low.\n\nA possible solution could be we try update first, if no row is updated insert it. But the problem for that is: if 2 requests are trying to update/insert the same shard, they may end up compete insert a row with the same primary key, and one of them will fail.",
